<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202826>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 18. Gymnolaelaps prestoni sp. nov., female. 10. dorsal shield; 11. opisthosomal seta enlarged; 12. ventral idiosoma; 13. hypostome; 14. palp tarsal claw; 15. epistome; 16. chelicera; 17. genu III, dorsal aspect; 18, genu and tibia IV, dorsal aspect. Scale bar = 100 μm for 10 and 12, 50 μm for 13, 15, 16, 17, 18; 10 μm for 14. Figure 11 not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202826/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

